ità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003528-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Bitto and Griffo.</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Sellios Praktikos and Likinia Kleite made this for themselves while living.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Griffo NSA 1942 82 no. 1 fig. 20 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Bitto 2001 19 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Slightly irregularly spaced thinly cut lunate Greek letters: lunate epsilon and sigma, cursive omega, terminations to many of the strokes.</p> Line 1-5  32-33  Interlineation line 1 to 5  5  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
